  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1: \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd? (LIVE)",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Presidential Election Today: Who Will Win? (LIVE)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa fled the country due to the country's insurgency, which plunged him into severe economic crisis. Ranil Wickramasinghe took over as interim president.",
        "In this case, the election to choose the new president will be held today, Wednesday. The names of Ranil Wickramasinghe, Dallas Alagamperuma and Anurakumara Dissanayake have been proposed in Parliament for the post.",
        "Opposition leader Sajith Premadasa, who was in the race for the post of President, has said that he will not contest for the post and has proposed the name of Dulles Beauty.",
        "Dallas Alagamperuma, 63, has held ministerial responsibilities since 2005. Another candidate, 53-year-old Anurakumara Dissanayake, belongs to the People's Liberation Front.",
        "This type of election of the President by Parliament is unprecedented since 1978. In 1982, 88, 94, 99 and in 2005, 2010, 2015 and 2019, the country has elected the President by popular vote.",
        "DB Wijetunga was unanimously elected by Parliament to fill the position left vacant in 1993 when then President Ranasinghe Premadasa was assassinated. After that, the President is to be elected by a vote in the Parliament.",
        "It is worth noting that the new president to be elected today will hold office until November 2024, the remaining term of Gotabaya Rajapaksa."
      ],
